{"tid":341578,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[乜撚都話有毒]到底煮食用具咩材料先安全","createTime":"2017-07-31T01:43:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-06T13:33:03.000Z","uid":61494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2ce039ee4daf23e9a89c5edb00edb4eaac00ce93","tid":341578,"uid":61494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T01:43:04.000Z","msg":"陶瓷: 有鉛、鎘<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20111224/15922279\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20111224%2F15922279&d=dGuZikqhVjJsCjegsLqG34sQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=79b07b3d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20111224%2F15922279&h=fb3b3ae1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20111224/15922279</a><br />\nLe Creuset陶瓷碗<br />\n含鉛超標280倍<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n搪瓷: 釋出鉛、錫和鎘等重金屬，飲用後會損害人體中樞神經系統，干擾免疫系統，導致慢性中毒，嚴重甚至會死亡。孕婦若吸收過量鉛，更可能誕下畸胎，甚至胎死腹中。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20061221/6641827\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20061221%2F6641827&d=dGuZikqhVjJsCjegsLqG34sQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=3e40b847\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20061221%2F6641827&h=87737e86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20061221/6641827</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n易潔鑊:  釋放化學物PFOA 乾煎易潔鑊 致癌物落肚<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20160328/s00005/1459100646398\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20160328%2Fs00005%2F1459100646398&d=dGuZikqhVjJsCjegsLqG34sQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=2e17cd06\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20160328%2Fs00005%2F1459100646398&h=8527435d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20160328/s00005/1459100646398</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不鏽鋼: 遇到「酸、鹼、或塩類較高的食物」極易釋出有毒的鎳和鉻。<br />\n<br />\n玻璃：<br />\n和陶瓷一樣，注意上釉和上光所使用的顏料。 <br />\n<br />\n琺瑯：<br />\n和陶瓷一樣，內部有著色的應該避免使用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你咁用乜先安全"},{"pid":"3e9354b7043e9fbb91d5ffb1de7f8fd99b7e5898","tid":341578,"uid":61494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T01:53:29.000Z","msg":"求教"},{"pid":"4c8abfa1c94212b707f7ef8f1c7546d1f35d4e64","tid":341578,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T01:55:15.000Z","msg":"其實宜家大部份貴價易潔都不含pfoa"},{"pid":"ca4bb0de68b725ef8c391bd1d94d6daa9105d10b","tid":341578,"uid":60404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T02:02:00.000Z","msg":"cast iron"},{"pid":"7222615598cc8305b09c93ae2dfb2f632a4d1909","tid":341578,"uid":59902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T02:03:36.000Z","msg":"真心有無易潔鑊牌子/ 型號介紹返"},{"pid":"bc3ba643cbf821353aed93c6557d66cee5cfd17a","tid":341578,"uid":59902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T02:04:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真心有無易潔鑊牌子/ 型號介紹返</blockquote><br />\n依家係出面行真係花多眼亂  同埋呢期好興哥d大理石面係咪都係柒野?"},{"pid":"f689bfe44c643f4319485088eb60e6dca7e6fdf9","tid":341578,"uid":61494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T02:56:32.000Z","msg":"我淨係想要安全煮個野食啫 <br />\n<br />\n唔係打手post唔講牌子只講物料"},{"pid":"4bde56632aa6819104a5f4a29985b9b6b90be3b5","tid":341578,"uid":21200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T03:43:12.000Z","msg":"用樹枝拮住燒"},{"pid":"3ca8d57f03735a666cda8fa8d31fb56e2bdb9864","tid":341578,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T03:57:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3f24c0729dac1aae38c4d574db0354f058572693","tid":341578,"uid":61494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T